def softmax(x):
    max_val = max(x)
    x_exp = [val - max_val for val in x]
    numerator = [0] / len(x)
    for i in range(len(x_exp)):
        numerator[i] = pow(10, x_exp[i])
    denominator = sum(numerator)
    softmax_vals = [0] * len(x)
    for i in range(len(x_exp)):
        softmax_vals[i] = numerator[i] / denominator
    return softmax_vals
